!!! 5
%html(lang="en-US")
  %head
    %title= "#{SITE_NAME}"
    = stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all'
    = csrf_meta_tags
    %meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, minimum-scale=1")
    %link(href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway:700,900' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css')
    %link(href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lora:400,700italic,700,400italic' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css')
    = yield :head
  %body

    %nav.admin_panel
      %ul
        %li= link_to Phil.name, "#"
        %li= link_to "create post", "#"
        %li= link_to "drafts", "#"
        %li= link_to "sign out", "#"

    %header.site_head
      %div
        %h1= link_to "Today I learned", "#"
        %h2= link_to "A Hashrocket project", "#"

    -# #flash
    -#   %p.notice= Phil.words 20
    -#   %p.error= Phil.words 20

    %main= yield

    %nav.site_nav
      %ul
        %li.site_nav__about
          = link_to "About TIL", "#", class: "site_nav__link"
          .site_nav__toggle
            .copy
              :markdown
                HA es una iniciativa de Kleer que visibiliza y comparte el conocimiento que adquirimos día a día y nuestras experiencias de aprendizaje. Los mensajes tienen un límite de 200 palabras y cualquier Kleerer puede contribuir. Esperamos que disfrutes aprendiendo junto con nosotros.

                HA está basado en [TIL](https://til.hashrocket.com/), un proyecto open-source del equipo de [Hashrocket](https://hashrocket.com)
              %ul.social
                %li= link_to "/hashrockettil", "http://twitter.com/hashrockettil", class: "social_twitter"
                %li= link_to "/hashrockettil", "http://github.com/hashrockettil", class: "social_github"
        %li.site_nav__statistics
          = link_to "statistics", "#", class: "site_nav__link"
        %li.site_nav__search
          %form<
            = link_to "search", "#", class: "site_nav__link"
            .site_nav__toggle
              %input(type='search')
              %input(type='submit' value='Search')

    = javascript_include_tag 'application'
